"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Performing Upgrades\\n\\n## Managing Upgrades\\n\\nValidators can choose how to run a validator and manage software upgrades according to their preferred option:\\n\\n1. Using [Cosmovisor](./cosmovisor.mdx)\\n2. Manual\\n\\n## Voting for Upgrade Proposals\\n\\nSee [Voting](../running-node/voting.mdx)\\n\\n## Upgrades\\n\\nReleases for the dYdX Chain will use [semantic versioning](https://semver.org/). See [here](./types-of-upgrades.mdx) for details.\\n\\n### ⚒️ Cosmovisor Users\\n\\n#### Upgrading to a new Major/Minor Version (e.g. v0.1.0)\\n\\n1. Download the [binary](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain) for the new release, rename the binary to `dydxprotocold`.\\n\\n```bash\\nmv dydxprotocold.<version>-<platform> dydxprotocold\\n```\\n\\n2. Make sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\n```bash\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n```\\n\\n3. Create a new directory `$DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/<name>/bin` where `<name>` is the URI-encoded name of the upgrade as specified in the Software Upgrade Plan.\\n\\n```bash\\nmkdir -p $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/<name>/bin\\n```\\n\\n4. Place the new binary under `$DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/<name>/bin` before the upgrade height.\\n\\n\\n```bash\\nmv <path_to_major_version> $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/<name>/bin\\n```\\n\\n💡 **IMPORTANT**: Do this before the upgrade height, so that `cosmovisor` can make the switch.\\n\\nThat's it! The old binary will stop itself at the upgrade height, and `cosmovisor` will switch to the new binary automatically. For a `Plan` with name `v0.1.0`, your `cosmovisor/` directory should look like this:\\n\\n```\\ncosmovisor/\\n├── current/   # either genesis or upgrades/<name>\\n├── genesis\\n│   └── bin\\n│       └── dydxprotocold\\n└── upgrades\\n    └── v0.1.0\\n        ├── bin\\n           └── dydxprotocold\\n```\\n\\n#### Upgrading to a Patch Version (e.g. v0.0.2)\\n\\n1. Download the [binary](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/releases) for the new patch release, rename the binary to `dydxprotocold`.\\n\\n```bash\\nmv dydxprotocold.<version>-<platform> dydxprotocold\\n```\\n\\n2. Make sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\n```bash\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n```\\n\\n3. Replace the binary under `$DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/current/bin` with the new binary.\\n\\n```bash\\nmv <path_to_patch_version> $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/current/bin\\n```\\n\\n4. Stop the current binary (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\n5. Restart `cosmovisor`\\n\\n```bash\\ncosmovisor run start --p2p.seeds=\\\"[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656\\\" --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=\\\"<eth rpc endpoint>\\\"\\n```\\n\\n### 🦾 Manual Users\\n\\n#### Upgrading to a Major/Minor Version (e.g. v0.1.0)\\n\\n1. Download the [binary](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/releases) for the new release.\\n    1. Ideally also before the upgrade height to minimize downtime\\n2. Make sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\n```bash\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n```\\n\\n3. Wait for the old binary to stop at the upgrade height (this should happen automatically).\\n4. Restart the application using the **new binary from step 1**.\\n\\n```bash\\n./dydxprotocold start --p2p.seeds=\\\"[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656\\\" --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=\\\"<eth rpc endpoint>\\\"\\n```\\n\\n#### Upgrading to a Patch Version (e.g. v0.0.2)\\n\\n1. Download the [binary](https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/releases) for the new release.\\n2. Make sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\n```bash\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n```\\n\\n3. Stop the current binary (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\n4. Restart the application using the new binary from step 1.\\n\\n```bash\\n./dydxprotocold start --p2p.seeds=\\\"[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656\\\" --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=\\\"<eth rpc endpoint>\\\"\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Rollback\\n\\n\\nIn the case of an unsuccessful chain upgrade, an incorrect `AppHash` might get persisted by Tendermint. To move forward, validators will need to rollback to the previous state so that upon restart, Tendermint can replay the last block to get the correct `AppHash`. **Please note:** validators should never rollback further than the last invalid block. In extreme edge cases, transactions could be reverted / re-applied for the last block and cause issues.\\n\\n\\n### ⚒️ Cosmovisor Users\\n\\nCosmovisor backs up the `data` directory before attempting an upgrade. To restore to a previous version:\\n\\n1. Stop the node (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\n2. Then, copy the contents of your backup data directory back to `~/.dydxprotocol`\\n\\n```bash\\nrm -rf ~/.dydxprotocol/data\\nmv ~/.dydxprotocol/data-backup-YYYY-MM-DD ~/.dydxprotocol/data\\n```\\n\\n3. Restart your node.\\n\\n```bash\\ncosmovisor run start --p2p.seeds=\\\"[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656\\\" --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=\\\"<eth rpc endpoint>\\\"\\n```\\n\\n### 🦾 Manual Users\\n\\nIf you don't have a data backup:\\n\\n1. Stop the node (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\n2. Rollback the application and Tendermint state by one block height.\\n\\n```bash\\n./dydxprotocold rollback\\n```\\n\\n3. Restart your node.\\n\\n```bash\\n./dydxprotocold start --p2p.seeds=\\\"[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656\\\" --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=\\\"<eth rpc endpoint>\\\"\\n```\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#performing-upgrades\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#performing-upgrades\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"Performing Upgrades\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#managing-upgrades\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Validators can choose how to run a validator and manage software upgrades according to their preferred option:</p>\\n<ol>\\n<li>Using <a href=\\\"./cosmovisor.mdx\\\">Cosmovisor</a></li>\\n<li>Manual</li>\\n</ol>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#managing-upgrades\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nValidators can choose how to run a validator and manage software upgrades according to their preferred option:\\n\\nUsing Cosmovisor\\nManual\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Managing Upgrades\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#voting-for-upgrade-proposals\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>See <a href=\\\"../running-node/voting.mdx\\\">Voting</a></p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#voting-for-upgrade-proposals\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nSee Voting\\n\",\"title\":\"Voting for Upgrade Proposals\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#upgrades\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Releases for the dYdX Chain will use <a href=\\\"https://semver.org/\\\">semantic versioning</a>. See <a href=\\\"./types-of-upgrades.mdx\\\">here</a> for details.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#upgrades\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nReleases for the dYdX Chain will use semantic versioning. See here for details.\\n\",\"title\":\"Upgrades\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#️-cosmovisor-users\",\"html\":\"\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#️-cosmovisor-users\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"⚒️ Cosmovisor Users\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Upgrades\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#upgrading-to-a-new-majorminor-version-eg-v010\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li>Download the <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain\\\">binary</a> for the new release, rename the binary to <code>dydxprotocold</code>.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">mv</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold.</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">versio</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">n</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">-</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">platfor</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">m</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"2\\\">\\n<li>Make sure that the new binary is executable.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">chmod</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> 755</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"3\\\">\\n<li>Create a new directory <code>$DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/&lt;name&gt;/bin</code> where <code>&lt;name&gt;</code> is the URI-encoded name of the upgrade as specified in the Software Upgrade Plan.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">mkdir</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> -p</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> $DAEMON_HOME</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">/cosmovisor/upgrades/</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">nam</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">e</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">/bin</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"4\\\">\\n<li>Place the new binary under <code>$DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/&lt;name&gt;/bin</code> before the upgrade height.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">mv</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> &lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">path_to_major_versio</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">n</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> $DAEMON_HOME</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">/cosmovisor/upgrades/</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">nam</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">e</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">/bin</span></span></code></pre>\\n<p>💡 <strong>IMPORTANT</strong>: Do this before the upgrade height, so that <code>cosmovisor</code> can make the switch.</p>\\n<p>That&#x27;s it! The old binary will stop itself at the upgrade height, and <code>cosmovisor</code> will switch to the new binary automatically. For a <code>Plan</code> with name <code>v0.1.0</code>, your <code>cosmovisor/</code> directory should look like this:</p>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">cosmovisor/</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">├── current/   # either genesis or upgrades/&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#22863A;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">name</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">&gt;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">├── genesis</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">│   └── bin</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">│       └── dydxprotocold</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">└── upgrades</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    └── v0.1.0</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">        ├── bin</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">           └── dydxprotocold</span></span></code></pre>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#upgrading-to-a-new-majorminor-version-eg-v010\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nDownload the binary for the new release, rename the binary to dydxprotocold.\\n\\nmv dydxprotocold.&lt;version&gt;-&lt;platform&gt; dydxprotocold\\n\\nMake sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n\\nCreate a new directory $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/&lt;name&gt;/bin where &lt;name&gt; is the URI-encoded name of the upgrade as specified in the Software Upgrade Plan.\\n\\nmkdir -p $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/&lt;name&gt;/bin\\n\\nPlace the new binary under $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/&lt;name&gt;/bin before the upgrade height.\\n\\nmv &lt;path_to_major_version&gt; $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/upgrades/&lt;name&gt;/bin\\n💡 IMPORTANT: Do this before the upgrade height, so that cosmovisor can make the switch.\\nThat&#x27;s it! The old binary will stop itself at the upgrade height, and cosmovisor will switch to the new binary automatically. For a Plan with name v0.1.0, your cosmovisor/ directory should look like this:\\ncosmovisor/\\n├── current/   # either genesis or upgrades/&lt;name&gt;\\n├── genesis\\n│   └── bin\\n│       └── dydxprotocold\\n└── upgrades\\n    └── v0.1.0\\n        ├── bin\\n           └── dydxprotocold\\n\",\"title\":\"Upgrading to a new Major/Minor Version (e.g. v0.1.0)\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Upgrades\",\"⚒️ Cosmovisor Users\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#upgrading-to-a-patch-version-eg-v002\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li>Download the <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/releases\\\">binary</a> for the new patch release, rename the binary to <code>dydxprotocold</code>.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">mv</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold.</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">versio</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">n</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">-</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">platfor</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">m</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"2\\\">\\n<li>Make sure that the new binary is executable.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">chmod</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> 755</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"3\\\">\\n<li>Replace the binary under <code>$DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/current/bin</code> with the new binary.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">mv</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> &lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">path_to_patch_versio</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">n</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> $DAEMON_HOME</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">/cosmovisor/current/bin</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"4\\\">\\n<li>Stop the current binary (e.g. Ctrl+C)</li>\\n<li>Restart <code>cosmovisor</code></li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">cosmovisor</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> run</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> start</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --p2p.seeds=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#upgrading-to-a-patch-version-eg-v002\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nDownload the binary for the new patch release, rename the binary to dydxprotocold.\\n\\nmv dydxprotocold.&lt;version&gt;-&lt;platform&gt; dydxprotocold\\n\\nMake sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n\\nReplace the binary under $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/current/bin with the new binary.\\n\\nmv &lt;path_to_patch_version&gt; $DAEMON_HOME/cosmovisor/current/bin\\n\\nStop the current binary (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\nRestart cosmovisor\\n\\ncosmovisor run start --p2p.seeds=&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot; --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;\\n\",\"title\":\"Upgrading to a Patch Version (e.g. v0.0.2)\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Upgrades\",\"⚒️ Cosmovisor Users\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#-manual-users\",\"html\":\"\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#-manual-users\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"🦾 Manual Users\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Upgrades\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#upgrading-to-a-majorminor-version-eg-v010\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li>Download the <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/releases\\\">binary</a> for the new release.\\n<ol>\\n<li>Ideally also before the upgrade height to minimize downtime</li>\\n</ol>\\n</li>\\n<li>Make sure that the new binary is executable.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">chmod</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> 755</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"3\\\">\\n<li>Wait for the old binary to stop at the upgrade height (this should happen automatically).</li>\\n<li>Restart the application using the <strong>new binary from step 1</strong>.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">./dydxprotocold</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> start</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --p2p.seeds=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#upgrading-to-a-majorminor-version-eg-v010\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nDownload the binary for the new release.\\n\\nIdeally also before the upgrade height to minimize downtime\\n\\n\\nMake sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n\\nWait for the old binary to stop at the upgrade height (this should happen automatically).\\nRestart the application using the new binary from step 1.\\n\\n./dydxprotocold start --p2p.seeds=&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot; --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;\\n\",\"title\":\"Upgrading to a Major/Minor Version (e.g. v0.1.0)\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Upgrades\",\"🦾 Manual Users\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#upgrading-to-a-patch-version-eg-v002-1\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li>Download the <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-chain/releases\\\">binary</a> for the new release.</li>\\n<li>Make sure that the new binary is executable.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">chmod</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> 755</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydxprotocold</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"3\\\">\\n<li>Stop the current binary (e.g. Ctrl+C)</li>\\n<li>Restart the application using the new binary from step 1.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">./dydxprotocold</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> start</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --p2p.seeds=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\\n<hr/>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#upgrading-to-a-patch-version-eg-v002-1\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nDownload the binary for the new release.\\nMake sure that the new binary is executable.\\n\\nchmod 755 dydxprotocold\\n\\nStop the current binary (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\nRestart the application using the new binary from step 1.\\n\\n./dydxprotocold start --p2p.seeds=&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot; --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Upgrading to a Patch Version (e.g. v0.0.2)\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Upgrades\",\"🦾 Manual Users\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#rollback\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>In the case of an unsuccessful chain upgrade, an incorrect <code>AppHash</code> might get persisted by Tendermint. To move forward, validators will need to rollback to the previous state so that upon restart, Tendermint can replay the last block to get the correct <code>AppHash</code>. <strong>Please note:</strong> validators should never rollback further than the last invalid block. In extreme edge cases, transactions could be reverted / re-applied for the last block and cause issues.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#rollback\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nIn the case of an unsuccessful chain upgrade, an incorrect AppHash might get persisted by Tendermint. To move forward, validators will need to rollback to the previous state so that upon restart, Tendermint can replay the last block to get the correct AppHash. Please note: validators should never rollback further than the last invalid block. In extreme edge cases, transactions could be reverted / re-applied for the last block and cause issues.\\n\",\"title\":\"Rollback\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#️-cosmovisor-users-1\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Cosmovisor backs up the <code>data</code> directory before attempting an upgrade. To restore to a previous version:</p>\\n<ol>\\n<li>Stop the node (e.g. Ctrl+C)</li>\\n<li>Then, copy the contents of your backup data directory back to <code>~/.dydxprotocol</code></li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">rm</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> -rf</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> ~/.dydxprotocol/data</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">mv</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> ~/.dydxprotocol/data-backup-YYYY-MM-DD</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> ~/.dydxprotocol/data</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"3\\\">\\n<li>Restart your node.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">cosmovisor</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> run</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> start</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --p2p.seeds=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#️-cosmovisor-users-1\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nCosmovisor backs up the data directory before attempting an upgrade. To restore to a previous version:\\n\\nStop the node (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\nThen, copy the contents of your backup data directory back to ~/.dydxprotocol\\n\\nrm -rf ~/.dydxprotocol/data\\nmv ~/.dydxprotocol/data-backup-YYYY-MM-DD ~/.dydxprotocol/data\\n\\nRestart your node.\\n\\ncosmovisor run start --p2p.seeds=&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot; --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;\\n\",\"title\":\"⚒️ Cosmovisor Users\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Rollback\"]},{\"href\":\"/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades#-manual-users-1\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>If you don&#x27;t have a data backup:</p>\\n<ol>\\n<li>Stop the node (e.g. Ctrl+C)</li>\\n<li>Rollback the application and Tendermint state by one block height.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">./dydxprotocold</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> rollback</span></span></code></pre>\\n<ol start=\\\"3\\\">\\n<li>Restart your node.</li>\\n</ol>\\n<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">./dydxprotocold</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> start</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --p2p.seeds=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;</span></span></code></pre>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/nodes/upgrades/performing-upgrades.mdx#-manual-users-1\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nIf you don&#x27;t have a data backup:\\n\\nStop the node (e.g. Ctrl+C)\\nRollback the application and Tendermint state by one block height.\\n\\n./dydxprotocold rollback\\n\\nRestart your node.\\n\\n./dydxprotocold start --p2p.seeds=&quot;[seed_node_id]@[seed_node_ip_addr]:26656&quot; --bridge-daemon-eth-rpc-endpoint=&quot;&lt;eth rpc endpoint&gt;&quot;\",\"title\":\"🦾 Manual Users\",\"titles\":[\"Performing Upgrades\",\"Rollback\"]}]}}"
